verbose_text: The results showed that the mRNA expression of Foxp3 in PDN group (1.82 +/- 0.06) was significantly higher than that in control group (1.12 +/- 0.08) (p < 0.01, Figure XREF_FIG a) and the mRNA expression of Foxp3 in PDN + CTK group (1.57 +/- 0.13) was significantly higher than that in CTK group (1.09 +/- 0.18) (p < 0.01, Figure XREF_FIG a).
